<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/message.asp?topic=55906366&replies=0">vnboards.ign.com/message....&replies=0</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Of course this might be a load of bull but I for one actually believe it.<br>
It feels that &quot;the skald remake&quot; has been within reach for months now and that with each patch Mythic snatched that carrot from right under our noses. Since they now have some new tools to play with regarding class and realmbalance maybe we are closer than ever?<br>
Lets all keep our fingers crossed we'll have a big tasty bite of that carrot this time!<br>
<br>
Anyhow, seems there is yet to be a reason for me to quit SWG to come back. I do appreciate the effort you guys put into this issue though and Rosie in particular! Bring on the letters and see what 1.65 brings!<br>
